all of Honduras|Honduras]])\n|report     = https://www.concacafnationsleague.com/en/nations-league/game-detail/476672\n|result     = L\n}}\n{{Football box collapsible\n|date       = 19 November\n|time       = 17:00\n|round      = [[2019\u201320 CONCACAF Nations League C| Nations League C]]\n|team1      = {{fb-rt|PUR}}\n|score      = 3\u20130\n|team2      = {{fb|AIA}}\n|goals1     =\n*[[Sidney Rivera|Rivera]] {{goal|56||67|pen.}}\n*[[Devin Vega|Vega]] {{goal|82}}\n|goals2     =\n|location   = [[Bayam\u00f3n, Puerto Rico|Bayam\u00f3n]], Puerto Rico\n|stadium    = [[Juan Ram\u00f3n Loubriel Stadium]]\n|attendance =\n|referee    = Ariel S\u00e1nchez ([[Panamanian Football Federation|Panama]])\n|report     = https://www.concacafnationsleague.com/en/nations-league/game-detail/476673\n|result     = W\n}}\n\n== Records ==\n=== Most capped players ===\n{{Updated|13 June 2017}}\n:''Players in '''bold''' are still active, at least at club level.''\n{{check quotation|reason=mismatched italics}}{| class=\"wikitable sortable\" style=\"font-size:90%; text-align:center;\"\n|-\n!width=\"50\"|#\n! style=\"width:150px;\"|Name\n! style=\"width:100px;\"|Career\n!width=\"50\"|Caps\n!width=\"50\"|Goals\n|-\n|rowspan=\"2\"|1\n|style=\"text-align: left;\"|'''[[H\u00e9ctor Ramos]]'''\n|2010\u2013\n|'''33'''\n|18\n|-\n|style=\"text-align: left;\"|'''[[Andr\u00e9s Cabrero]]'''\n|2008\u2013\n|'''33'''\n|4\n|-\n|2\n|style=\"text-align: left;\"|[[Alexis Rivera Curet|Alexis Rivera]]\n|2004\u20132016\n|'''31'''\n|0\n|-\n|3\n|style=\"text-align: left;\"|'''[[Joseph Marrero]]'''\n|2011\u2013\n|'''28'''\n|6\n|-\n|4\n|style=\"text-align: left;\"|[[Noah Delgado]]\n|2008\u20132012\n|'''23'''\n|3\n|-\n|5\n|style=\"text-align: left;\"|[[Cristian Arrieta]]\n|2010\u20132015\n|'''22'''\n|5\n|-\n|6\n|style=\"text-align: left;\"|[[Chris Megaloudis]]\n|2008\u20132012\n|'''20'''\n|6\n|-\n|7\n|style=\"text-align: left;\"|[[Andr\u00e9s P\u00e9rez (footballer, born 1988)|Andr\u00e9s P\u00e9rez]]\n|2011\u20132015\n|'